1) James Crippen discover a bug in 3.38, writing\
\
"I am reliably experiencing delays in switching to the editor window in\
\pard\pardeftab720
\cf0 the latest TeXShop. The delays are 2 to 3 seconds long. The focus\
shifts off of whatever other window I was on and the editor window\
comes forward, but it does not highlight until the delay is complete.\
The cursor also does not appear, and I don\'92t see any text I type until\
the delay is over. The system may switch spaces back to the window if\
I\'92ve switched spaces during the delay."\
